/decl/cultural_info/faction/umco
	name = FACTION_MARINES
	description = "(PLACEHOLDER) Universal Marine Corps Organisation, or UMCO for short and often refered as just UMC, is \
	a controversial union of private military companies, known for contracting battle-capable (and rank-obedient) humans and \
	other species for amphibian and expeditionary security and combat purposes. It uses old Marine ranks for ease of command, \
	as well as their tactics, behavior and ways in general, to the point of being living seterotype. \
	Because founders originally been in SCG Army, many of UMCO still using Sol Government Military uniforms, \
	despite many protests from SCG."
